    public class Stump
extends javax.swing.JButton
    Models a stump. This class represents a JButton object of a stump. When combined with the Create map class, instances of the Stump class can be displayed on the window.

        参数:
        stumpX - The x-coordinate of the stump on the screen.

        isEnd - The flag to indicate whether reach the end.

      • initialConnected

        public void initialConnected​(CreateMap map)

        参数:
        map - The corresponding level of map
